OL,3,CWarning issued after mountain fire
OL,4,Ccaused by unattended campfire
OL,6,FA wildfire caused by an unattended
OL,7,Fcampfire has seen fire chiefs urge
OL,8,Fmembers of the public to enjoy the
OL,9,Fcountryside responsibly.
OL,11,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fsent three crews and two wildfire
OL,13,Funits to tackle a fire on a
OL,14,Fmountainside at Dwygyfylchi, Conwy,
OL,15,Fafter being alerted at 7.27pm on
OL,16,FTuesday, 20 August.
