OL,3,CWarning issued after mountain fire
OL,4,Ccaused by unattended campfire
OL,6,FThe service said the fire, which is
OL,7,Fthought to have affected around a
OL,8,Fquarter of an acre, is thought to have
OL,9,Fbeen caused by a campfire left
OL,10,Funattended.
OL,12,FTim Owen, from North Wales Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Service, said: "We are
OL,14,Fencouraging everyone to be wildfire
OL,15,Fwise and commit to simple precautions
OL,16,Fand take a little extra care to help
OL,17,Fensure we can continue to enjoy our
OL,18,Fbeautiful countryside and keep our
OL,19,Fcommunities safe from the devastating
OL,20,Feffects of wildfire.
