OL,3,CWarning issued after mountain fire
OL,4,Ccaused by unattended campfire
OL,6,F"During this time of year, grass and
OL,7,Fmountains can become very dry, which
OL,8,Fmeans if you deliberately or
OL,9,Faccidentally start a fire outdoors it
OL,10,Fwill spread very quickly, destroying
OL,11,Feverything in its path.
OL,13,F"We are encouraging all members of our
OL,14,Fcommunities to respect our countryside
OL,15,Fand play their part in safeguarding
OL,16,Four environment and keeping our
OL,17,Fcommunities safe.
