OL,3,CWarning issued after mountain fire
OL,4,Ccaused by unattended campfire
OL,6,F"While accidents do happen, they are
OL,7,Falso often avoidable, and our Wildfire
OL,8,FWise campaign focuses on educating us
OL,9,Fall on some of the small steps we can
OL,10,Ftake to ensure we don't accidentally
OL,11,Fcause a grass fire to ignite."
OL,13,FAdvice to help protect the countryside
OL,14,Fincludes ensuring all barbecues are
OL,15,Fdiscarded appropriately, not burying
OL,16,Fthem in sand, and disposing of
OL,17,Fbottles, glasses and broken glass to
OL,18,Favoid them magnifying the sun and
OL,19,Fpotentially starting a fire.
